OL,3,CThe faces behind the campaign for a
OL,4,Cfresh Summerland inquest
OL,6,FSince the 50th anniversary of the
OL,7,FSummerland fire, a number of survivors
OL,8,Fand bereaved families have joined
OL,9,Fforces to form a campaign - calling
OL,10,Ffor a fresh inquest into the blaze.
OL,12,FMembers are fighting to overturn the
OL,13,Fdeath by misadventure verdict placed
OL,14,Fon those who lost their lives in the
OL,15,Ffire, something campaigners say puts
OL,16,Fthe blame on the victims who lost
OL,17,Ftheir lives at Summerland.
