OL,3,CThe faces behind the campaign for a
OL,4,Cfresh Summerland inquest
OL,6,FA total of 50 people died, and 80 more
OL,7,Fwere seriously injured, following a
OL,8,Ffire in the island's leisure complex
OL,9,Fon 2 August 1973.
OL,11,FThe campaign was formed during the
OL,12,F50th anniversary of the fire, where
OL,13,Fsurvivor Jackie Hallam began to
OL,14,Faddress her trauma surrounding the
OL,15,Fdisaster for the very first time.
OL,17,FIt sparked a movement that has since
OL,18,Fgained MPs support in Westminster, and
OL,19,Fa lawyer fighting on behalf of the
OL,20,Fgroup.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
