OL,3,CThe faces behind the campaign for a
OL,4,Cfresh Summerland inquest
OL,6,FJackie was just 13-years-old when she,
OL,7,Fher mother Lorna and her friend Jane
OL,8,Fwere caught at the centre of the
OL,9,FSummerland fire.
OL,11,FBoth Lorna and Jane died in the blaze,
OL,12,Fbut Jackie managed to escape in
OL,13,Fhorrific circumstances that still
OL,14,Fhaunt her to this day.
OL,16,FFor half a century, she was unable to
OL,17,Ftalk about the fire.
