OL,3,CThe faces behind the campaign for a
OL,4,Cfresh Summerland inquest
OL,6,FBilly, 18, and his friend David, 17,
OL,7,Fwere on holiday in the Isle of Man,
OL,8,Fafter enjoying visiting the island in
OL,9,Fprevious years.
OL,11,FThe pair have been described as
OL,12,F'lifetime friends', and both lost
OL,13,Ftheir lives in the Summerland fire.
OL,15,FBilly's sister Stella has joined
OL,16,Fvoices for a new inquest into the fire.
OL,18,FRichard Barber is the youngest son of
OL,19,FAnne, known fondly as Nancy.
