OL,3,CThe faces behind the campaign for a
OL,4,Cfresh Summerland inquest
OL,6,FAnne tragically died inside the
OL,7,FSummerland leisure complex, along with
OL,8,Fher 'dearest friend' Elsie Stevens.
OL,10,FRichard, and his closest family
OL,11,Fmembers have since joined calls to
OL,12,Foverturn the misadventure verdict
OL,13,Fplaced on those who died.
OL,15,FThese are just some of those calling
OL,16,Fon the Isle of Man to hold a fresh
OL,17,Finquest into the Summerland fire, with
OL,18,Fmany wishing to remain anonymous.
